result.name: Genome assembly resources of genitourinary cancers for chromosomal aberration at the single nucleotide level
result.description: We obtained high-fidelity (HiFi) long-read sequencing data of six genitourinary tumor cell lines (PC-3, DU 145, LNCaP, Caki-1, HK-2, SNU1272) using the PacBio Revio system.
result.center: Department of Convergent Bioscience and Informatics
